		<td><b>Re: Arcade-perfect &quot;Pac-Man&quot; version?</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Pithily, a copy of MAME on your choice of computer.<br /><br />The original PacMan arcade machine was Z80-based, so I'd arbitrarily guess that machines that had more in common with that (e.g. SMS, Spectrum) have a better chance of duplicating the mechanics, due to being able to reuse larger portions of the original code.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


